{"tid":1875173,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對香港已經絕望⋯","createTime":"2020-02-11T15:14:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T07:55:33.000Z","uid":231980,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4a43b73c12975395606f4ec476435110fa104865","tid":1875173,"uid":231980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T15:14:31.000Z","msg":"六月到而家 <br />\n經歷過幾多次情緒低落、 失控爆喊 ⋯ <br />\n可以做到嘅都做晒<br />\n<br />\n而家睇新聞直頭睇到有反胃嘅感覺<br />\n點解香港人要咁慘？ <br />\n點解個政府咁撚樣都仲有一班傻閪藍精靈係度跳舞開P打邊爐 ⋯ <br />\n點解可以醫護出黎救港都仲有人鬧？ 仲要俾人批鬥？<br />\n點解班黑警成晒魔， 殺人滅口、 唔撚使做， 仲要拎盡資源？ <br />\n<br />\n以前我成日都諗人善有好報， 平常心面對 ，有天理嘅。<br />\n<br />\n咁點解而家仲未報？<br />\n<br />\n係，我無錢移民 <br />\n係，我無能力救世人<br />\n係，我咩都做唔到 <br />\n<br />\n唉 好撚灰 ，好撚絕望 ⋯"},{"pid":"f8e511b3fce68a01ca76b989a4e4dfacc63540ea","tid":1875173,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T15:17:00.000Z","msg":"我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好想走"},{"pid":"d7232acd2f1f447a798826ecf2ad8dd1b3e53495","tid":1875173,"uid":179139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T15:18:19.000Z","msg":"報應永遠都來得比較遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望有命見證到報應嘅來臨<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"641ab546c85656384f93fcf8d2c1b3dd7a9eb047","tid":1875173,"uid":231980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8e511b3fce68a01ca76b989a4e4dfacc63540ea","tid":1875173,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T15:17:00.000Z","msg":"我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好想走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T15:18:59.000Z","msg":"好撚灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n計黎計去 ⋯ 計唔掂呀 <br />\n<br />\n移左民長老點算？ <br />\n<br />\n唔移仲生唔生 <br />\n唔生都唔知點生活， 何況生⋯"},{"pid":"91a315e12fbe8971913f4624d6eabeab99c004a9","tid":1875173,"uid":6667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T1